<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-T3c6CoIi6uLrA9TneNEoa7RxnatzjcDSCmG1MXxSR1GAsXEV/Dwwykc2MPK8M2HN" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.1.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <link href="https://unpkg.com/aos@2.3.1/dist/aos.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/landingPage.css">
    <title>PingPal</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div id="main">
        <div class="navbar">
            <h1 class="siteName">PingPal</h1>
            <div class="navlinks">
                <a href="#home">Home</a>
                <div class="dropdown">
                    <a id="dropdown" class="btn btn-secondary dropdown-toggle" href="#" role="button" data-bs-toggle="dropdown" aria-expanded="false">
                      Features
                    </a>
                  
                    <ul id="dropdown-menu" class="dropdown-menu">
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#browser">Browser Compatibility</a></li>
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#data-synchronized">Data Synchronzation</a></li>
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#emoji-sticker">Emoji's & Stickers</a></li>
                      <li><a class="dropdown-item" href="#customer-service">Customer Service</a></li>
                    </ul>
                  </div>
                <a href="#contact-us">Contact us</a>
            </div>
            <a href="/login" id="login">Chat</a>
        </div>
        <div id="home">
            <div class="home-left">
                <h1 class="heading-home">Welcome to our Web Chat App</h1>
                <p class="desc-home">where seamless communication meets effortless connectivity. With our intuitive interface and powerful features, staying connected with friends, family, and colleagues has never been easier. Whether you're catching up with loved ones or collaborating on projects, our web chat app provides the perfect platform for meaningful conversations. Join us and experience the future of online communication today!</p>
            </div>
            <img class="chatting-img" src="images/chat.png" alt="Image of person chatting">
        </div>
        <div id="browser" style="min-height: 100vh;">
            <img id="browser-img" data-aos="fade-right"
                 data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                 data-aos-duration="800" src="./images/browserCompatibility.png" alt="compatible to all browsers image"></img>
            <div class="browser-right">
                <h1 data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800">
                    Browser Compatibility
                </h1>
                <p data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800"
                data-aos-delay="200">
                Enjoy uninterrupted chatting across all major web browsers. Whether you prefer Chrome, Firefox, Safari, or Edge, the Web Chat App ensures a consistent and reliable experience.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="data-synchronized" style="min-height: 100vh;">
            <div class="data-synchronized-left">
                <h1 data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800">
                    Data Synchronzation
                </h1>
                <p data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800"
                data-aos-delay="200">
                Keep your conversations in sync across all your devices. Chat history, settings, and preferences seamlessly transfer between your desktop, laptop, tablet, and smartphone
                </p>
            </div>
            <img class="data-synchronized-img" src="images/dataSynchronization.png" alt="Use over multiple devices" data-aos="fade-left"
            data-aos-easing="ease-in-out" data-aos-duration="800">
        </div>
        <div id="emoji" style="min-height: 100vh;">
            <img id="emoji-img" data-aos="fade-right"
                 data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                 data-aos-duration="800" src="./images/emojiSupport.png" alt="compatible to all browsers image"></img>
            <div class="emoji-right">
                <h1 data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800">
                    Emoji Support
                </h1>
                <p data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800"
                data-aos-delay="200">
                Add flair to your messages with a diverse range of emojis. Express emotions, reactions, and sentiments vividly, enhancing the richness of your conversations
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="customer-service">
            <div id="customer-service-img" data-aos="fade-right"
            data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
            data-aos-duration="800"></div>
            <div class="customer-service-right">
                <h1 data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800">
                    24x7 Customer Support
                </h1>
                <p data-aos="fade-up"
                data-aos-easing="ease-in-out"
                data-aos-duration="800"
                data-aos-delay="200">
                    Lorem ipsum dolor sit, amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Sit facilis odit tenetur aliquam vitae fugiat ad! Dolor doloribus deleniti, pariatur amet, perspiciatis beatae quo repellendus possimus totam omnis tempora labore asperiores explicabo? Ipsam ea labore nostrum provident. Architecto fugit quaerat voluptatibus aut, cupiditate expedita quam adipisci quasi iste tenetur unde.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="contact-us" style="min-height: 40vh;">
            <div class="support">
                <div class="support-left">
                    <h1>Contact Us:</h1>
                    <p><b>Toll free number:</b> 1800-7553-73</p>
                    <p><b>Email us at:</b> support@pingpal.com</p>
                </div>
                <div class="support-right">
                    <h2>Useful Links</h2>
                    <a href="#home">Home</a>
                    <a href="#browser">Features</a>
                    <a href="/pingpal/chat">Start Chatting</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="support-bottom">
                <p>2024 &copy PingPal</p>
                <a href="#"> Terms and Policy </a>
                <div class="socials">
                    <i class="ri-facebook-circle-line icons"></i>
                    <i class="ri-instagram-line icons"></i>
                    <i class="ri-linkedin-line icons"></i>
                    <i class="ri-youtube-line icons"></i>
                    <i class="ri-twitter-x-line icons"></i>
                    <i class="ri-discord-line icons"></i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

<!-- scripts -->
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/gsap/3.12.5/gsap.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/bodymovin/5.7.12/lottie.min.js"></script>
<script type="module" src="./javascripts/landingPage.js"></script>
